{"type": "article", "id": 25598, "title": "扎哈用黑色花岗岩设计的书架", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-18T07:08:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115101sdEf4ncqBRVZx3rX.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是扎哈和意大利石材公司 CITCO 合作的书架，使用了黑色花岗岩做成 4 个型号不同的模块。每一块可以看做是一个线条，从中间向左右或上面的墙面延伸，拥有扎哈所特有的流动的曲线。这种流动性体现出的轻盈与厚重的花岗岩构成对比，很有艺术感。4 个模块的架子可以任意搭配在一起，这个系列与扎哈产品设计的风格是类似的，<a href=\"http://www.citco.it/en/zaha-hadid\">点击这里</a>可查看她与  CITCO 合作的产品设计。<br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115059f0E7FiYysqo9tK5U.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71271394\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115059ls8nHJjvB5UoP2zZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.07823961\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115100w4XUIvYLOju57B13.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115100Nsx8Kv4UimH37QR1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115100hSWMZFAR5cKaG08C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}